channel.title: Connection Recieved from
channel.description:
When I run server it say "[b]Connection Recieved From: [/b] _______________"(ip)
I tried with three other people And when ever they try to log on it says [b]unexpected server response[/b] By the way Im using a 508 server source.
I figured the problem out for me
IF your gonna play a 508 source you must play with a 508 client (no silab is not.)
Download umairs Works wonders
